      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# AI Security Analysis With RAG\nThe prepared source code is sent to an AI Agent. The agent uses OpenRouter as the LLM and Pinecone as a secure-coding knowledge tool, supported by Gemini embeddings, to reason over vulnerabilities and remediation.",
        "height": 816,
        "width": 592,
