      "name": "Sticky Note3"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Patch and Verification Flow\nThe AI output is parsed into structured fields: findings, patched source, unified diff, and verification details. IF nodes check whether vulnerabilities were found and whether a patch was generated.",
