        "content": "# Report, Audit, and Output\nThe workflow generates a Markdown security report containing findings, risk, impact, vulnerable LOC, patched code, and verification status. Results can be logged to Google Sheets, and the final output is returned depending on whether the input came from webhook or form upload.",
